  <h4><a href="/new-potatoes-with-butter-and-soy-sauce-shinjaga-shouyu-bataa#comment-6693" class="active">New potatoes</a></h4>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi there, I have not thought butter and soya sauce will go well together. I will definitely try. I also now live in, Basel, Switzerland. I tried the very tiny ones once in Alsace, they were lovely. I have a small bottle of Sansho bought from 100Yen shop but do not really know what food will go well with it. Thx for the recipe. Thx Janet</p>
