<div class="comment odd clear-block">

  

  <h4><a href="/new-potatoes-with-butter-and-soy-sauce-shinjaga-shouyu-bataa#comment-6697" class="active">Confession</a></h4>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Maki, ever since I started reading your site I knew the time would come when I had to admit something to you. As a little girl growing up in the US I loved rice. I like it just about anyway it was cooked.  But my all time favorite topping was soy sauce and butter! Ever since I&#8217;ve started reading Japanese food blogs I&#8217;ve felt so ashamed about that, LOL. This recipe made me feel a little bit better about loving the combination.</p>
  </div>

